The following companies are having
unusual price changes in Argentine trading. Stock symbols are in
parentheses and share prices are as of 11:52 a.m.  New York  time.  The Merval Index fell 0.2 percent to 3,157.45.  Petroleo Brasileiro SA (PETR4)  , the oil and gas producer,
dropped 1.2 percent to 71.75 pesos. Crude oil fell in New York
on speculation that global demand is weakening.  Siderar SAIC (ERAR)   slipped 1.6 percent to 27.75 pesos.
